<div class="headtop">Shamus Young Dot Com</div>

<div class="headcontent">
<div class="headtext">
<div class="aboutimage"><img src="images/boom_headshot.jpg" width="150"/></div>
<div class="about">I'm Shamus Young, a programmer, an <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Witch-Watch-Shamus-Young/dp/1470105810">author</a>, 
and nearly a <a href="https://soundcloud.com/shamusyoung">composer</a>. 

I have produced an unbelievable volume of 
content over the years. If you're looking for the newest stuff, then <a href="twentysidedtale/">read the blog</a>, 
which has updated an average of once a day since 2005. But if you're looking for just the good stuff, then you 
can cherry-pick from the articles below. Enjoy!
</div>
</div>

